summary: Last night I dreamt that @danielhowell told me he was housesitting for my boss and wanted me to go with. Of course I said sure,...
body:
Last night I dreamt that @danielhowell told me he was housesitting for my boss and wanted me to go with. Of course I said sure, it’s dani snot on fire for crap’s sake. So we get to my boss’s swanky mansion and Dan’s acting suspicious as all hell, and when my boss and his family pull in the driveway he tells me to hide and I’m like… “Dan… did we break into my boss’s home?”


Dan just starts weeping, my intimidating boss finds us, and were sent to court, but the jury is a bunch of 1st graders on a field trip and I tell them it was all Dan’s fault. He starts weeping harder, but dude, it was the truth.


So Dan went to prison and I took a lovely stroll through a park filled with ponies and called it a day.
